      "bookmarkId": "3300029367_8_2507-2578",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2507-2578",
      "markText": "我们只知道现在是混乱时代，断不是和平统一时代，政治是只有更反动更混乱的；但这是和平统一的来源，是革命的生母，是民主独立的圣药，大家不可不知道。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029367&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2507&rangeEnd=2578",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/037322a0813ab71f8g017df1?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2507&rangeEnd=2578"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029367_4_1738-1780",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1738-1780",
      "markText": "激烈方法的共产主义，即所谓劳农主义，用阶级专政的方法，是可以预计效果的，故最宜采用。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1738&rangeEnd=1780",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/037322a0813ab71f8g017df1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1738&rangeEnd=1780"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029367_13_1589-1640",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1589-1640",
      "markText": "一般国家主义派，盛倡其“为祖国而牺牲，乃无上光荣”的说法，这是资产阶级欺人之话，我们万不要受他们的愚弄",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029367&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1589&rangeEnd=1640",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/037322a0813ab71f8g017df1?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1589&rangeEnd=1640"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029367_4_1678-1701",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1678-1701",
      "markText": "无政府主义否认权力，这种主义恐怕永世都做不到。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029367&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1678&rangeEnd=1701",
